        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Cost-Share Accountability Act of 2022</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Energy to report on the use of its authority to reduce or eliminate the cost-sharing requirements for its research, development, demonstration, and commercial application program or activities under the Energy Policy Act of 2005.</p>]]>
        </text>
